    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME OVERVIEW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Detective Nielsen. Good that you're here. We've got a homicide.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You're a detective in the first real VR investigation game in 1986 in New Orleans.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city and interrogate unforgettable characters in this unique take on a classic Point&amp;Click adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A man was murdered. Not just any man. John Malone, a promising city council member. Step into a world where every cigarette holds a clue, and every whiskey glass reflects a lie. In this groundbreaking VR experience, you're more than just a player – you're the detective who might crack the case...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMMERSE YOURSELF IN DETECTIVE WORK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/4023000114c807d98bd9da0d20934bb4.poster.avif?t=1738074054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/4023000114c807d98bd9da0d20934bb4.webm?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/4023000114c807d98bd9da0d20934bb4.mp4?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore photorealistic environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/f0915295ae0fef42dd1fcf982877af51.poster.avif?t=1738074054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/f0915295ae0fef42dd1fcf982877af51.webm?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/f0915295ae0fef42dd1fcf982877af51.mp4?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interrogate and question lifelike characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/8b790737e872a334e1f7b17691209765.poster.avif?t=1738074054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/8b790737e872a334e1f7b17691209765.webm?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282790/extras/8b790737e872a334e1f7b17691209765.mp4?t=1738074054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find clues that other players won't</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
